<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/tech_riders_logo.jpg" type="image/x-icon" />
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AyuLinker - Traditional Medicine Mapping Platform</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
  <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/@google/model-viewer/dist/model-viewer.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.13.0/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <%- include("navbar") %>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="main-content">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1>Discover Traditional Medicine Mappings with AI-Powered Precision</h1>
          <p>
            AyuLinker bridges NAMASTE and ICD-11 TM2 terminology systems using
            FHIR-compliant APIs, ensuring faster, standardized, and error-free
            integration of traditional and modern medical classifications.
          </p>
          <a href="/search-page" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px">
            <div class="card shadow p-3 card-hover model-container" style="border-radius: 16px">
              <h6 class="text-center mb-3" style="text-align: start">🌿 Medicinal Plant Leaf</h6>
              <model-viewer id="glb" src="/models/leaves/generic-leaf.glb" alt="Generic medicinal leaf" auto-rotate
                camera-controls shadow-intensity="1" exposure="1" style="
                  width: 100%;
                  height: 400px;
                  min-height: 350px;
                  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
                  border-radius: 12px;
                ">
                <div slot="poster" style="
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    justify-content: center;
                    height: 100%;
                    color: #666;
                    background: #f8f9fa;
                    border-radius: 12px;
                  ">
                  <div style="text-align: center">
                    <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px">🌿</div>
                    <div>Loading 3D Model...</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; margin-top: 5px">
                      Interactive leaf visualization
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </model-viewer>
              <div class="mb-3 text-center">
                <small class="text-muted">Interactive 3D model of medicinal plant leaf</small>
              </div>
              <div class="leaf-label">AYURVEDA: Jwara (ज्वर)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem and Solution Section -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="content-container">
        <div class="problem-solution-grid">
          <!-- Problem Card -->
          <div class="info-card problem-card">
            <h2>Problem in Hand </h2>
            <div class="problem-content">
              <p><strong>Manual integration of NAMASTE and ICD-11 TM2 codes into EMRs is:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Time-consuming</span> and <span class="highlight">error-prone</span></li>
                <li>Leads to inconsistent and unverified medical records</li>
                <li>Creates poor interoperability with India’s EHR Standards</li>
                <li>Increases administrative load for AYUSH hospitals and clinics</li>
              </ul>
              <p><strong>Root causes include:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Linguistic variations and differing traditional medicine terminology</li>
                <li>Lack of standardized workflows for code mapping</li>
                <li>Frequent updates in ICD-11 and NAMASTE needing constant remapping</li>
                <li>Manual processes that hinder scalability, analytics, and policy use</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Solution Card -->
          <div class="info-card solution-card">
            <h2>How AyuLinker Solves It</h2>
            <div class="solution-content">
              <p>
                <span class="highlight">AyuLinker</span> is a FHIR-compliant micro-service that
                automatically connects NAMASTE codes with WHO’s ICD-11 TM2 and biomedical
                categories through real-time synchronization and AI-powered mapping.
              </p>

              <div class="solution-feature">
                <div class="feature-icon">🌿</div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                  <h4>AI + Standards</h4>
                  <p>Dual-coding engine that bridges traditional and biomedical terms seamlessly.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <div class="benefit-icon">✓</div>
                  <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h5>Automated FHIR Resource Generation</h5>
                    <p>Generates CodeSystem, ValueSet & ConceptMap automatically from CSVs.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <div class="benefit-icon">✓</div>
                  <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h5>Real-Time ICD-11 Sync</h5>
                    <p>Fetches updates directly from WHO’s ICD-11 API for TM2 and biomedicine.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <div class="benefit-icon">✓</div>
                  <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h5>Smart Chatbot</h5>
                    <p>Suggests the most probable disease based on symptoms using NLP.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <div class="benefit-icon">✓</div>
                  <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h5>FHIR $translate Endpoint</h5>
                    <p>Enables two-way mapping for EMR integration with ABHA-secured access.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-item">
                  <div class="benefit-icon">✓</div>
                  <div class="benefit-text">
                    <h5>Analytics Dashboard</h5>
                    <p>Displays real-time AYUSH morbidity trends for research and policy use.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Started & Download Section -->
    <section class="get-started-section">
      <div class="content-container get-started-container">
        <div class="text">
          <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Transform Traditional Medicine Digitally?</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Join AyuLinker today and enable seamless dual coding between NAMASTE and ICD-11.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/register" class="cta-button">Register Now</a>
        <br />
        <div class="text">
          <h2 class="section-title">Download the App</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">Quick access for practitioners and researchers.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/app/AyuLinker.apk" class="cta-button">Download Now</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="content-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why AyuLinker is a Game Changer</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">No deep ML or NLP expertise needed — plug and play FHIR service.</p>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="first-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🧬</div>
              <h3>FHIR-Compliant Terminology Service</h3>
              <p>
                Built on HL7® FHIR R4 with CodeSystem, ValueSet & ConceptMap APIs for EMR
                interoperability.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">⚙️</div>
              <h3>Dual Coding Engine</h3>
              <p>
                Stores NAMASTE and ICD-11 codes together in a single patient record, ensuring
                standardization.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
              <h3>Real-Time Sync</h3>
              <p>
                Continuous synchronization with WHO ICD-11 API ensures latest TM2 updates are reflected.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bottom-2">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
              <h3>Data Analytics Dashboard</h3>
              <p>Visualize dual-coded data for insurers, researchers, and policymakers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">☁️</div>
              <h3>Cloud Ready</h3>
              <p>Deployable on cloud or on-premises with Docker scalability and high availability.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
              <h3>Symptom-Based Chatbot</h3>
              <p>
                AI-powered assistant that predicts possible conditions and suggests ICD-11 TM2 mappings.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="content-container faq-container">
        <div class="faq-main">
          <h2 class="section-title faq-item">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4 class="faq-question">How accurate is AyuLinker’s term mapping?</h4>
            <p class="faq-answer">
              AyuLinker’s auto-mapping engine ensures 90%+ initial accuracy by leveraging verified NAMASTE and ICD-11 datasets.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4 class="faq-question">Can it integrate with existing EMRs?</h4>
            <p class="faq-answer">
              Yes, our RESTful FHIR APIs allow seamless plug-in with major EMR systems supporting OAuth 2.0 authentication.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4 class="faq-question">Does it support multiple traditional systems?</h4>
            <p class="faq-answer">
              Yes, AyuLinker supports Ayurveda, Unani, Siddha, and other traditional systems recognized by the Ministry of AYUSH.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4 class="faq-question">Is it secure?</h4>
            <p class="faq-answer">
              All communications are secured via OAuth 2.0, ABHA tokenization, and ISO-22600 consent management.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="model">
          <h3 class="chatbot-heading" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary-blue); cursor: pointer;">
            🤖 Double-click on the astronaut to chat with him
          </h3>
          <model-viewer id="glb" class="faq-3d" src="/models/leaves/astronaut-on-suit.glb" alt="3D Astronaut" auto-rotate
            camera-controls shadow-intensity="1" exposure="1" style="
              background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
              border-radius: 12px;
            ">
          </model-viewer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('footer') %>

  <script src="/js/hamburger.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/index-animation.js"></script>

